{"tid":918042,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"侵爺暗示提高關稅至 25% 幾乎勢在必行 蘋果iPhone和筆電或徵 10%","createTime":"2018-11-27T01:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T03:40:14.000Z","uid":13663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51bc013aa8a120bed2258dd034ecdbf3af8bd434","tid":918042,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"川普提高關稅至 25% 幾乎勢在必行 蘋果iPhone和筆電或徵 10%<br />\n<br />\n2018/11/27 07:10<br />\n鉅亨網編譯羅昀玫<br />\n(圖：AFP)<br />\n(圖：AFP)<br />\n美國總統川普週一 (26 日) 接受《華爾街日報》採訪時表示美國「極不可能」推遲提高關稅，意味著明年 1 月 1 日對 2000 億美元中國輸美商品提高關稅 (至 25%) 勢在必行；考量到消費者反應，蘋果手機和筆電或許將課徵 10%，此消息一出，拖累蘋果盤後股價應聲下跌。<br />\n<br />\nA<br />\n週一蘋果盤後股價應聲下跌 1.35%。<br />\n中國官員此前表示，川習會首要任務是說服美國暫停「 1 月 1 日起中國進口 2000 億美元商品關稅從目前的 10% 上調至 25 %。」然而，川普對此回應：「美國不太可能同意。」<br />\n川普還提到，如果 G20 川習會談判無效，將對目前尚未受關稅影響的其他中國進口產品課徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n川普表示：「如果我們未達成協議，那麼將對剩餘 2670 億美元中國商品開徵關稅，稅率為 10% 或 25%。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然可以對從中國進口的 iPhone 和筆記型電腦徵收關稅，但美國政府一直對消費者的反應感到擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n針對蘋果的手機和筆記本電腦課稅問題，川普提到：「也許這取決於利率是多少，我可以把課稅 10%，人們便可以很容易地接受。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，川普還再次呼籲美企鮭魚返鄉，在美國建廠及生產產品。他說：「美國企業還有很多其他選擇。」"},{"pid":"816effca54a2f20ab9d3896c2b065ee1e75b48e4","tid":918042,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"好好享受最後的盛宴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed46ad7eb904e338fbb5bc3f8a156471ec18c15","tid":918042,"uid":40356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:31:41.000Z","msg":"未試過咁期待一個國際會議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d310cb8150619d1c5b241181404e81e47a7a25c","tid":918042,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"希望習種響同侵侵嘅會議上，一槍打瓜侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d12f7f31f5b3ee0d822923ce5c10831dcd749af","tid":918042,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"其實未到最後一刻都好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604ba9e7b431e389ea1359d8356f4b4ec6e20089","tid":918042,"uid":1369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"下年買iPhone 要20k先得"},{"pid":"bd4298e4d8e6c47c3f7fd2c7eac29fef3767a8b0","tid":918042,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"604ba9e7b431e389ea1359d8356f4b4ec6e20089","tid":918042,"uid":1369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"下年買iPhone 要20k先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"先達狗要運iphone去美國炒？"},{"pid":"7b9de5928be9b534985e4bb0c362bcfd4add4e63","tid":918042,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d310cb8150619d1c5b241181404e81e47a7a25c","tid":918042,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"希望習種響同侵侵嘅會議上，一槍打瓜侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NP00wPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNP00wPh.png&h=f2013047&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91e10611077c9de7bc50aa8c06954e8d7b0cdf82","tid":918042,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"又可以見證歷時刻<br />\n果然英雄造時勢"},{"pid":"89f607ad7ae927c8ed672d099e11176aed473b8e","tid":918042,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}